nmap <M-=> <zoomIn>
nmap <M--> <zoomOut>
nmap <M-[> <toLastUsedTab>
nmap <M-n> <toNextSplitWindow>
nmap <M-p> <toPreviousSplitWindow>
nmap <M-1> <toFirstSplitWindow>
nmap <M-0> <toLastSplitWindow>
nmap <M-l> <rotateSplitWindowForward>
nmap , <decreaseWidthSplitWindow>
nmap ; <decreaseHeightSplitWindow>
